
---
const SITE_TITLE = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SITE_TITLE ?? 'EcoVision';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>About {SITE_TITLE}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
    }
    main {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: auto;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    h1, h2 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    @media (min-width: 480px) {
      main {
        padding: 30px;
      }
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #555;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <h1>About {SITE_TITLE}</h1>
    <p>{SITE_TITLE} empowers communities to document environmental hazards and promotes awareness, advocacy, and action. By reporting issues like illegal dumping, polluted water, and unsafe drainage, citizens help track environmental patterns and push for sustainable solutions.</p>

    <h2>Why Use {SITE_TITLE}?</h2>
    <p>Community participation is the core of our platform. Each report contributes to a broader understanding of local environmental challenges. Together, we can monitor trends, highlight urgent issues, and advocate for cleaner, safer neighborhoods.</p>

    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>{SITE_TITLE} is community-driven. We do not verify user submissions. Data is solely for environmental monitoring. We do not guarantee responses or action from authorities. Users are responsible for their own safety.</p>

    <a href="/">← Back to Home</a>
    <p class="footer">© 2025 {SITE_TITLE} — All Rights Reserved</p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>